How can I claim the ad credit from Clickbank?

To redeem an ad credit on NewsBreak, you need to create an account and choose the Prepay billing option. If your campaign costs exceed your ad credit balance, you'll need a valid credit card linked to your account to cover the remaining amount. For more detailed instructions, please check out this article: [How to redeem a NewsBreak ad credit](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17391456255629-How-to-redeem-a-NewsBreak-ad-credit). Let me know if you have any other questions!
